{"tid":484045,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"誰不捨我難過","createTime":"2017-11-29T17:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T09:11:05.000Z","uid":74139,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f807c51825d14625f6f831d9d4c79c88cf58bf3b","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"心裏依然住了一個誰，但再回顧從前跟你的合照和對話時，我再也不懂笑，而是過份地念掛落淚。最可悲莫過於，只有自己還在執著，對方是多麼慶幸拋下這個負累，去準備擁抱新生活了。"},{"pid":"2c65e86fa8b76b80c02839ccbc71a5037c0966e5","tid":484045,"uid":83682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc102c9995fc03c959be5c256029d4158cbed660","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:50:49.000Z","msg":"每天經過的油麻地站，當天在此與他聊得樂不可支；偶爾踏足的沙田站，曾經在此與他分享上班的苦與樂；不再走近的奧運站，昔日在此與他牽手走過每一段路。不知不覺已走了多遠，如今回首卻是觸得到的近。"},{"pid":"766ed749f0985232d35ff8e3d7b2169a35d4fa64","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:54:47.000Z","msg":"儘管曾經有過很多不愉快，我依然很感激遇到他。那段日子讓我暫忘生活中的繁瑣事，讓我找到一點認真過活的動力。即使他在分離之際的身影已變得模糊，我還是會偶爾憶起，與他初相見的那十秒。他闖進我的生命，並從未離去。"},{"pid":"e4f18d87c0b834c1494f14471d4d7cc2e16952aa","tid":484045,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都係住奧運"},{"pid":"e08724510245d024b004bfa8c0befdfdd75e9faf","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都係住奧運</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住但唔會再去了"},{"pid":"4556e917146dac105c328dbc10c53b62e86219c3","tid":484045,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b71945ed78e7fd87b152b8e555ab244a55adc61","tid":484045,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T21:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都係住奧運</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住但唔會再去了</blockquote><br />\n好掛住日日係mk送佢行返去個段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e55a6f2b1fc97c7019a9c715af23d42c5baf33","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"隔了好久才再次在playlist點播Mia &amp; Sebastian's Theme。<br />\n「如果相識是一種緣份，那分離亦不是一場巧合。」世事就是如此難料，你從不知道，此刻在你身邊的人，也許在下一秒就消失於你的世界。我們無法預知未來，與其執著於此，倒不如回想當初的心悸，只有留住回憶才能保存那已逝去的情感。<br />\n謝謝他，曾成為我的La La Land。"},{"pid":"1c4d43e4492d25ced81943fb0d973541edd8d953","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"從前你總嘲笑我，說我只是你的過路人。現在我想，人一生如此漫長，也沒有誰能陪你走到最後，說到底，每個人都是生命中的過客，只是有人停留的比較久而已。擁有多久也好，終究還是歸零，我唯有這樣安慰自己。<br />\n我好想你啊。"},{"pid":"95c8a5e5ed1a4b157314d9663c2789b79c512806","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"大抵沒有什麼比黑夜裏的情緒氾濫更難受。心胸很痛，思緒很亂，睡覺是我唯一的解脫。只是，如果破曉一刻打開眼，黑夜的淚痕還在，我寧願一睡不醒。"},{"pid":"152cc7d35dc582959e4b947e7278d11fc6ec03ed","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"生日快樂，祝你幸福。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d091f9bd64de762e8cec859e9c110c9ba9784859","tid":484045,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大抵沒有什麼比黑夜裏的情緒氾濫更難受。心胸很痛，思緒很亂，睡覺是我唯一的解脫。只是，如果破曉一刻打開眼，黑夜的淚痕還在，我寧願一睡不醒。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f51432608c9854316e85202f8fc7fda16cd43ae","tid":484045,"uid":40509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:18:05.000Z","msg":"今天是妳和他開始的第一天<br />\n請準我用好朋友的角色祝福妳"},{"pid":"d36bb0b9c69d18aa30eecfbf3108d118750354a0","tid":484045,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"他不將妳放心上...<br />\n即使再善良，未得到景仰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab7797f3378195145858bbad11407db308911de","tid":484045,"uid":65652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"加油"}]}